data.description: The QUINTESSENTIAL LITTLE BEACH HOUSE you've been looking for! This 2bd, 3/4 ba home provides everything you need for comfortable living. Large front porch deck. Beautiful open beam wood ceilings give a rustic, but airy feel. On the main floor, is a large living/dining area with a wood stove to cozy up to during stormy nights. Open concept kitchen, primary bedroom, large bathroom, laundry rm & extra finished room w/door to backyard where you can hear the crashing waves of the Pacific. Upstairs, is room for office space or game area & an XTRA large bdrm with French doors to a newly constructed deck with a peek-a-boo ocean view. Home is part of the Ocean Shores Community Club-annual Dues $165.
